(1103, 1, '2013-07-05 14:24:38', '2013-07-05 12:24:38', '[heading title="Alcune delle misure disponibili."]\r\n\r\nDi seguito solo alcune delle misure disponibili. Siamo in grado di realizzare borse di qualsiasi misura.\r\n\r\n[accordion]\r\n\r\n[accordion-item title="Tessuto / TNT - Cotone"]\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img class="wp-image-508 alignnone" style="margin: 0 10px 10px 0; border: 1px solid grey;" alt="04" src="http://www.arteastucci.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/043-150x150.jpg" width="120" height="120" /></td>\r\n<td>mis. (38x42)cm - (40x50)cm\r\nPREZZO da preventivare</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n[/accordion-item]\r\n[accordion-item title="TNT Argento/Oro Lucide"]\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img class="wp-image-508 alignnone" style="margin: 0px 10px 10px 0px; border: 1px solid grey;" alt="04" src="http://www.arteastucci.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/034-150x150.jpg" width="120" height="120" /></td>\r\n<td>mis. (34x7x36)cm - (30x10,5x33)cm\r\nPREZZO da preventivare</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n[/accordion-item]\r\n[accordion-item title="Kraft"]\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img class="wp-image-508 alignnone" style="margin: 0px 10px 10px 0px; border: 1px solid grey;" alt="04" src="http://www.arteastucci.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/036-150x150.jpg" width="120" height="120" /></td>\r\n<td>mis. (18x8x24)cm - (22x10x29)cm - (27x12x37)cm - (32x12x45)cm - (45x15x49)cm - (49x17x54)cm\r\nPREZZO da preventivare in base alla quantità</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n[/accordion-item]\r\n[accordion-item title="Elegant"]\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img class="wp-image-508 alignnone" style="margin: 0px 10px 10px 0px; border: 1px solid grey;" alt="04" src="http://www.arteastucci.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/06-150x150.jpg" width="120" height="120" /></td>\r\n<td>mis. (10x5x18)cm - (13,5x6x2)cm - (20x10x26)cm - (20x12x36)cm - (20x9x32)cm - (24x9x38)cm - (33x10x24)cm - (36x12x45)cm\r\nPREZZO da pre